Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Course
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is responsible for modelling a course which details the attributes and methods of each * Course object part of the STARS Planner system.
